===============

### Mixed Boat Trailers Contract

#### Solicitation Details

* **Reference Number**: PW-22-01015491
* **Amendment Number**: 01
* **Solicitation Number**: W8476-236612/B
* **Publication Date**: 2022-12-01
* **Tender Closing Date**: 2023-01-05T14:00:00
* **Amendment Date**: 2022-12-05

#### Contracting Entity Information

* **Contracting Entity Name** (English): Department of National Defence
* **Contracting Entity Address** (English): 101 Colonel By Dr, Ottawa, Ontario, K1A0K2, Canada
* **Contracting Entity Name** (French): Ministère de la défense nationale
* **Contracting Entity Address** (French): 101, promenade Colonel By, Ottawa, Ontario, K1A0K2, Canada

#### Contact Information

* **Contact Name**: Kyle Grundy
* **Contact Email**: kyle.grundy@forces.gc.ca
* **Contact Phone**: None

#### Tender Description

The Department of National Defence (DND) is soliciting proposals for the delivery of a mixed fleet of 18 boat trailers and In-Service Logistics (ILS) products to various locations across Canada. The requested delivery date is 120 days from Contract Award.

Please note that the Competition and Trade Agreement (CETA) requirements must be included in the tender description, if applicable. The estimated duration of the contract is from 01-29-2023 to 12-20-2023, and the delivery timeframe is from 04-01-2023 to 06-01-2023.

#### Attachments

The following attachments are available for download:

* Amendment 1 (English): https://canadabuys.canada.ca/documents/pub/att/2022/12/05/ae53c3dbfce55b26b50e17a0c6fa309c/en-amendment001-w8476-236612b.pdf
* Amendment 1 (French): https://canadabuys.canada.ca/documents/pub/att/2022/12/05/9aa1a27cb057870eab712f7872725bfb/fr-amendment001-w8476-236612b.pdf
* RFP (English): https://canadabuys.canada.ca/documents/pub/
